*

* This contains several macros for arpeggiating chords.

* Pass 3 notes and how many times to play them to arp3.

* Pass 4 notes and how many times to play them to arp4.

*

format  systems

macro   arp3 A B C D

*

* A,B,C are the notes -- D is the number of times to

* them

*

vars    i

loop    i ^= 1, D

        A B C

endloop

endmacro

*

macro   arp4 A B C D E

*

* A,B,C,D are the notes -- E is the number of times to

* them

*

vars    i

loop    i ^= 1, E

        A B C D

endloop

endmacro































































































































